00:29:13.880 --> 00:29:16.280
That's across a few applications though,

00:29:16.280 --> 00:29:20.680
and some are more RAM heavy than this is,

00:29:20.680 --> 00:29:23.079
although this is still pretty heavy.

00:29:23.079 --> 00:29:25.479
