00:29:36.880 --> 00:29:39.880
You can play with the settings and connect

00:29:39.880 --> 00:29:43.280
how eager versus unwilling it is

00:29:43.280 --> 00:29:45.680
to spin up a new session for incoming users.

00:29:45.680 --> 00:29:48.680
So you can have more people piled onto the same process

00:29:48.680 --> 00:29:50.680
or you can have more processes.

00:29:50.680 --> 00:29:53.479
It's some experimentation.

00:29:53.479 --> 00:29:55.680
There's also shiny cannon.

00:29:55.680 --> 00:29:58.079
I think that's the search term you want to use

00:29:58.079 --> 00:30:04.680
to do some testing, but that's at least our experience.

