00:33:14.680 --> 00:33:17.479
and this takes a lot of work

00:33:17.479 --> 00:33:19.479
and sort of institutional familiarity

00:33:19.479 --> 00:33:20.880
to actually make it stick,

00:33:20.880 --> 00:33:23.880
but we've been doing this for, you know, 15 years or so now.

00:33:23.880 --> 00:33:25.479
