We have a Teams channel of our users.

00:54:43.479 --> 00:54:47.479
It's fairly decentralized as far as I can tell.

00:54:47.479 --> 00:54:50.479
There are different offices that have their own teams

00:54:50.479 --> 00:54:53.479
that focus on their own functions.

00:54:53.479 --> 00:54:56.479
So there's not, at least not that I'm connected to,

00:54:56.479 --> 00:55:01.479
there's not a large centralized data science in VA organization.

